OL,4,CMenelik Shabazz: Tributes to 'pioneer
OL,5,Cof Black British filmmaking'
OL,6, Tributes have been paid to pioneering
OL,7, black British film-maker Menelik
OL,8, Shabazz, who has died at the age of 67.
OL,10,FShabazz was best known for his 1981
OL,11,Ffilm Burning an Illusion, which saw him
OL,12,Fbecome only the second black director
OL,13,Fof a British-made feature.
OL,15,FHis family described him as "a
OL,16,Fpassionate film-maker who forged the
OL,17,Fway for others" and Bafta called him "a
OL,18,Fpioneer of Black British filmmaking".
OL,20,FShabazz also founded The Black
OL,21,FFilmmaker Magazine.
